name: Michelle's Dolls
description: Star Babies, handmade by Michelle. This photo shows samples. Each doll is an individual, handmade, with organic and natural materials. She makes several different kinds of dolls ranging from $24 to $120 (6" - 18"). Custom dolls can be made to order. Shipping costs are paid by the buyer.

name: Beeswax Crayons
description: 16 vibrant colors in a tin box. Beeswax crayons are fun to use and look beautiful on the paper. These larger crayons are not as brittle as the typical grocery store brands and last much longer. Block crayons are available for younger children. Shipping is billed per cost.

name: Beeswax Candles
description: Shaped like a beehive, these beeswax candles purify the air, smell good and are beautiful as well. Locally made near Anchorage. Also available in a smaller size. Additional beeswax candles available, including tapers and tea lights. Shipping is billed according to cost.
